name: PRESA FÁCIL / EASY PREY
description: "PRESA FÁCIL" (trad. EASY PREY), is a "video-performance" which aims to criticize the "Brazillian White-Middle-Man", who is so lobotomized, that becomes a "Easy Prey" to the imperialist claws of the north. / moscô dançô / Video from 2019 / 1080 x 1920 / GABRIEL KOI / OBRJKT
